K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:167a-1: a'arya ga na pa ti hri da ya /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:167a-3: 'phags pa tshogs kyi bdag po'i snying po /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:167a-5: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:167a-6: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa dus gcig na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:167a-7: bcom ldan 'das rgyal po'i khab na bya rgod phung po'i ri la dge slong stong nyis brgya lnga bcu'i dge slong gi dge 'dun chen po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:167a-8: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sha stag dang thabs cig tu bzhugs te; de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo la bka' stsal pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:167b-0: gang la la tshogs kyi bdag po tshogs kyi dbang @167b phyug gi snying po 'dzin na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:167b-1: de'i las thams cad 'grub par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:167b-2: de bzung bas dgos pa 'grub cing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:167b-3: gsang sngags thams cad kyang dngos grub tu 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:167b-5: na mo stu te ma h'a ga na pa t'a ye sv'ah'a /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:168a-2: dge bsnyen ma gang la lja zhig chogs kyi bdag kho tshogs kyi dbang phyug gi snying po 'di rtsom zhing gsang sngags bsgrubs pas /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:168a-3: dkon mchog gsum mchod du yul gzhan du 'gro 'am /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:168a-4: rgyal po'i pho brang 'khor du 'jug na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:168a-5: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la me tog dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:168a-6: bdug pas mchod pa byas te tshogs kyi bdag po'i snying po 'di bklags na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:168a-8: 'di la the tshom ma za zhig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:168a-12: yul 'khrugs pa thams cad kyi nang du yang dran par byas na; thams cad rab tu zhi bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:168a-13: nyin gcig bzhin du nang par langs nas tshig tu bton na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:168a-17: mkha' 'gro ma thams cad kyis mdangs 'phrog par mi 'gyur zhing /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:168a-18: thag ring por yongs su spong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:168a-19: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:168a-20: thams cad dang ldan pa'i 'khor de dag dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-019:168b-0: dri zar bcas pa'i @168b 'jig rten yid rangs te bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do //
